1
00:00:05,860 --> 00:00:08,623
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,623 --> 00:00:12,178
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,178 --> 00:00:18,271
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,271 --> 00:00:24,397
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,397 --> 00:00:31,018
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,018 --> 00:00:36,104
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,104 --> 00:00:43,104
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,104 --> 00:00:48,428
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,428 --> 00:00:49,941
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,941 --> 00:00:55,704
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,704 --> 00:01:00,604
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:00,604 --> 00:01:08,471
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,471 --> 00:01:11,886
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,699
It's been a whole day.

15
00:01:24,699 --> 00:01:26,699
Have you made a decision?

16
00:01:27,099 --> 00:01:28,800
About what?

17
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,000
I'll give you another chance.

18
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:33,220
Tell me nicely, are we friends?

19
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:36,280
Xiaowen, get in the car. Let my dad take you home.

20
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:38,200
What kind of car is that? And taking him home?

21
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:41,059
Who's talking to you?

22
00:01:41,059 --> 00:01:43,200
Xiaowen, don't always hang out with poor students.

23
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:46,220
They're going to pull down your level.

24
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:52,519
Come on.

25
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,680
How awkward!

26
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:59,200
Stop pestering him. He's not like you.

27
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,979
You guys won't even go to the same university in the future.

28
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:07,579
Wanwan, get in the car.

29
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:22,860
Why are those from the elite class so pompous?

30
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:26,039
Every time the teacher explains the problem, they'd ask, "Do you understand now?"

31
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:30,980
And they will say, "We understand. You don't have to explain it anymore. Let's study by ourselves."

32
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:33,879
But the problem is that I still don't understand it.

33
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:37,740
Ask Xiaowen then. Aren't you two in the same class?

34
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:40,479
How can I approach Xiaowen?

35
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:42,600
Niu Wanwan is watching over him.

36
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,199
Niu Wan...

37
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:46,439
They are sitting next to each other.

38
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:48,620
What's Xiaowen's attitude to it?

39
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:57,060
Do you think Xiaowen takes us as his friends?

40
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:02,580
Why are still asking that? It's too obvious.

41
00:03:02,580 --> 00:03:05,680
Really? Analyze it for me then.

42
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,459
What's wrong?

43
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,759
Jia,

44
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:16,759
what's going on?

45
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:19,580
Okay, you go ahead.

46
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:31,179
- Jia.
- What are you looking at? Opening your eyes so big, what are you looking at?

47
00:03:31,179 --> 00:03:33,080
Don't hang out with the good students.

48
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:35,151
Are you good enough? Are we good enough?

49
00:03:35,151 --> 00:03:39,033
[Episode 12: Our Stubbornness]

50
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:44,120
Our class is flexible and competitive.

51
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:47,719
If your grades fall behind in one placement test,

52
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:50,999
you'll be replaced by a student in a normal class.

53
00:03:50,999 --> 00:03:53,180
It's brutal.

54
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:54,960
Therefore, you should all remember.

55
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:57,660
You're not here to make friends.

56
00:03:57,660 --> 00:04:01,059
Your failure means someone else's success.

57
00:04:01,059 --> 00:04:02,059
Do you understand?

58
00:04:02,059 --> 00:04:03,360
Yes!

59
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:07,840
Also, we can't have less homework than the others.

60
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:10,139
Instead, we'll have more.
[Believing and Reaching Makes You Calm, Elegant and Pure]

61
00:04:10,139 --> 00:04:13,999
For every problem the other students solve, you must complete a set of problems.

62
00:04:13,999 --> 00:04:18,940
Therefore, Niu Wanwan, hand out these ten sets of problems to your classmates after class.

63
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:21,520
I'll check them tomorrow, okay?

64
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:24,600
Okay, let's start our lesson now.

65
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:39,320
Where's Xiaowen?

66
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:44,200
Put down your stinky foot!

67
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:46,359
Are you going to eat that banana?

68
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,600
I'm asking you. Where's Xiaowen?

69
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,360
Don't ask me about everything.

70
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:54,120
Wait, what's going on with you two? You haven't been talking lately.

71
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:58,160
He's so high and mighty now. I wouldn't dare to disturb him.

72
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:00,060
You sound so jealous.

73
00:06:00,060 --> 00:06:01,399
Go and call Xiaowen back home.

74
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:04,059
He needs nourishment before the competition.

75
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:07,659
Ye Xiaowen, time for your nourishment.

76
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,840
What was that?

77
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:14,720
Go downstairs and yell for him. Hurry up and go!

78
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:21,159
Ye Xiaowen, time for your nourishment!

79
00:08:03,239 --> 00:08:08,700
Dawei, don't read your magazines all the time. The college entrance exam is around the corner.

80
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:12,120
Listen to Mr. Gao and go study.

81
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,580
Don't mention Mr. Gao again.

82
00:08:14,580 --> 00:08:17,399
What's wrong with mentioning Mr. Gao? He is my friend, too.

83
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,879
I'll mention him if I want to.

84
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,879
You can't stop me.

85
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:23,239
Don't let Gao Bin come to our place anymore.

86
00:08:23,239 --> 00:08:26,559
Dawei, what should I say about you?

87
00:08:26,559 --> 00:08:29,480
Mr. Gao came to our house to give us his sincere apologies.

88
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:33,260
You were dismissed because of the fight. What does that have to do with him?

89
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:35,799
Don't think I have no idea about what you did in school.

90
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,799
You even beat up his son.

91
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:41,279
Mr. Gao didn't mention a word of that and he even apologized to us.

92
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:44,600
If Mr. Gao takes the matter seriously, you would be expelled from the school.

93
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,600
Just keep being arrogant!

94
00:08:47,959 --> 00:08:50,579
I never wanted to go to this school anyway.

95
00:08:50,579 --> 00:08:52,240
I'm not done talking yet! Come back here!

96
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,119
Hurry up. It's your turn.
[Gangzi Repair Shop]

97
00:08:54,119 --> 00:08:56,399
Tell me. What should I do about that child?

98
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:58,099
Is it my turn?

99
00:08:58,099 --> 00:09:00,139
I win!

100
00:09:03,639 --> 00:09:05,639
I finally won!

101
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,320
What are you moaning about?

102
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:20,359
I'm fine. Just go to sleep.

103
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,659
What's going on?

104
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,000
What happened?

105
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,519
Nothing.

106
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,999
- Does your leg have a cramp?
- No.

107
00:09:37,999 --> 00:09:39,800
Let me see.

108
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:41,999
Slowly, slowly.

109
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,400
Relax.

110
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:46,659
Yes, take it easy.

111
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,720
Wait, why is it so stiff?

112
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,799
Just yell if it hurts.

113
00:09:53,939 --> 00:09:55,100
Look at you.

114
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:58,019
Just one competition is making you nervous like this.

115
00:09:58,019 --> 00:09:59,619
What do you know?

116
00:09:59,619 --> 00:10:00,679
What don't I know?

117
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:04,720
You want to attend Beijing University of Technology but the tuition is too expensive.

118
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,200
Don't worry.

119
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:09,840
Even if you don't get first place, Gao Bin will put you through college.

120
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:13,359
He will be very happy to see his child become a student at a famous college.

121
00:10:13,359 --> 00:10:15,580
I don't want to trouble anyone.

122
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:18,559
Aren't you troubling me now?

123
00:10:22,340 --> 00:10:24,840
Rely on your siblings at home and rely on your friends outside.

124
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,640
It's very normal.

125
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:31,700
That's enough. You can't help me.

126
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:34,160
What can't I help you with?

127
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,919
You can't help me. If I said you can't help me then it means you can't.

128
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:38,919
Then tell me about it.

129
00:10:42,519 --> 00:10:43,480
Say it.

130
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:46,260
I'm not doing this for myself.

131
00:10:46,260 --> 00:10:48,259
Who are you doing this for then?

132
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:54,619
For the children in the orphanage.

133
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,859
We all don't have parents.

134
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:02,140
We've always helped each other.

135
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:05,020
I need to earn money

136
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:07,960
and put them through college.

137
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:13,559
Alright, alright. Go back to sleep.

138
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:15,659
I still have to train tomorrow.

139
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,900
Thanks.

140
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:47,960
That Old Jin. Where do I find people within a week?

141
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:50,540
Besides, the ones we have at school are not enough.

142
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:55,579
Gao Bin, can you not come to my house anymore?

143
00:11:55,579 --> 00:11:56,440
Dawei, you're here.

144
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:59,240
I'm talking to you. Did you hear me? Don't come to my house anymore!

145
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:02,519
I heard you. Sit down for a bit. Let's chat for a while.

146
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,819
Don't leave.

147
00:12:08,159 --> 00:12:10,000
I went to your house

148
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,000
because

149
00:12:13,799 --> 00:12:16,620
I wanted to apologize to you.

150
00:12:16,620 --> 00:12:19,279
I found out about the fight afterwards.

151
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:21,639
I've misunderstood you.

152
00:12:23,879 --> 00:12:26,719
As a teacher, I'm quite a failure.

153
00:12:26,719 --> 00:12:28,839
I ruined your future.

154
00:12:28,839 --> 00:12:32,574
You're about to take the college entrance exam soon, but there isn't much I can do for you.

155
00:12:32,574 --> 00:12:34,959
But if...

156
00:12:34,959 --> 00:12:38,320
if you need anything, if you're upset about anything, or even if you want to yell at me,

157
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:40,560
you can come to me at any time.

158
00:12:59,639 --> 00:13:04,040
This is a set of comprehensive enhancement mock exams

159
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:08,260
I organized for everyone based on the college entrance exam questions for the past ten years.

160
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:13,219
Finish them and hand them in tomorrow.

161
00:13:13,219 --> 00:13:15,195
I'll check them tomorrow.

162
00:13:17,919 --> 00:13:23,319
Classmate. Classmate, these questions weren't printed clearly. Can I see yours?

163
00:13:23,319 --> 00:13:25,619
Go ask the teacher yourself.

164
00:14:10,039 --> 00:14:11,480
What is it? Are you looking for me?

165
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,600
It's nothing. I'm just passing by.

166
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,879
Wait. You... If you were passing by, then why were you standing here?

167
00:14:14,879 --> 00:14:17,063
Come on in. Let's talk for a while. Come in.

168
00:14:18,059 --> 00:14:20,359
Come in. Come.

169
00:14:20,359 --> 00:14:23,699
How is it going? Did you run into any problems?

170
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:29,559
Look at how you're just keeping everything to yourself.

171
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:31,959
Just tell me if there's a problem.

172
00:14:38,499 --> 00:14:42,140
Xiaowen, don't think that just because I have been the grade leader for a short period

173
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:45,960
I can't tell that you're very eager to excel.

174
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,279
And you work so hard too.

175
00:14:47,279 --> 00:14:48,679
Why are you doing that?

176
00:14:48,679 --> 00:14:51,500
You don't want to trouble anyone, right?

177
00:14:52,559 --> 00:14:58,259
See? But I must tell you that sometimes, you have to trouble other people.

178
00:14:58,259 --> 00:15:01,000
You can't handle everything yourself. How exhausting that is!

179
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:04,380
You need to have an intimate friend where you can help each other out.

180
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:08,519
Look at the first class of students I taught, they were typical examples.

181
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:10,720
At the time, they wanted to create a support group.

182
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,960
Other people said it will never work and it will certainly cause problems.

183
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:15,679
Wu Zhixun was the best in class and Li Qingtong was a poor student.

184
00:15:15,679 --> 00:15:17,720
The two of them helped each other and progressed together. Right?

185
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,999
That... That's a living example.

186
00:15:19,999 --> 00:15:21,279
They are all here.

187
00:15:21,279 --> 00:15:23,600
That's why you can't keep to yourself all the time.

188
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:26,020
You need to have... have someone you can confide in.

189
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:28,180
You can tell me anything.

190
00:15:31,399 --> 00:15:32,559
Thank you, Mr. Wu.

191
00:15:32,559 --> 00:15:33,919
That's right. You...

192
00:15:33,919 --> 00:15:36,120
Just speak without reserve with me, okay?

193
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:38,020
I'll be on my way now.

194
00:15:40,559 --> 00:15:45,290
Wait, let's talk for a while. Did I say all that in vain?

195
00:15:45,290 --> 00:15:47,410
[Grade 2, Class 3]

196
00:15:47,410 --> 00:15:49,440
"The following is my credo:

197
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:55,579
All I really need to know about how to live and what to do and how to be
[Credo by Fulghum]

198
00:15:55,579 --> 00:15:57,360
I learned in kindergarten.

199
00:15:57,360 --> 00:16:00,639
Wisdom was not at the top of the graduate-school mountain,

200
00:16:00,639 --> 00:16:04,179
but there in the sandpile at Sunday School.
[In your orphanage...]

201
00:16:04,179 --> 00:16:06,759
These are the things I learned:
[In your orphanage...]

202
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:08,919
Share everything.
[How was your orphanage like?]

203
00:16:08,919 --> 00:16:10,120
Play fair.
[How was your orphanage like?]

204
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,440
Don't hit people.

205
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,720
Don't take things that aren't yours.

206
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:16,360
Say you're sorry when you hurt somebody.

207
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:18,399
Wash your hands before you eat.

208
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:20,159
Flush.

209
00:16:20,159 --> 00:16:23,360
Warm cookies and cold milk are good for you.

210
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:25,320
Live a balanced life.

211
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:30,159
Learn some and think some and draw and paint and sing

212
00:16:30,159 --> 00:16:32,580
- It's for Mi Jia. Don't look.
- and dance and play

213
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:34,879
and work every day some.

214
00:16:34,879 --> 00:16:36,840
Take a nap every afternoon.

215
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,720
Believe in miracles.

216
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:42,920
Remember the little seed in the Styrofoam cup:

217
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:48,660
The roots go down and the plant goes up and nobody really knows how or why,

218
00:16:48,660 --> 00:16:52,139
but we are all like that.

219
00:16:52,139 --> 00:16:59,320
Goldfish and hamsters, white mice and even the little seed in the Styrofoam cup, they all die.

220
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:01,020
So do we."

221
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:09,360
There are a lot of children in our orphanage, some are older and some are younger.
[Sunshine Orphanage]

222
00:17:09,360 --> 00:17:12,340
Our dean used to be a teacher too.

223
00:17:12,340 --> 00:17:15,319
She took care of us with her own savings.

224
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:18,200
She has been the dean for over a decade.

225
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:23,400
The orphanage became bigger and bigger and it took in more and more children.

226
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:27,279
- Xiaowen, come get more if you're not full.
- The dean's savings were not nearly enough.

227
00:17:27,279 --> 00:17:30,279
Thank you, Dean.

228
00:17:30,279 --> 00:17:32,440
Mi Jia, is this enough?

229
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:35,600
Okay, I'll give you some more.

230
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:46,079
Children, let's welcome our older brothers and sisters home.

231
00:17:46,079 --> 00:17:47,979
Welcome, everyone.

232
00:17:49,359 --> 00:17:50,599
Very good.

233
00:17:50,599 --> 00:17:54,440
Everyone look, your older brothers and sisters brought us so many gifts.

234
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,839
Are you all happy?

235
00:17:55,839 --> 00:17:59,440
Yes!

236
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:02,039
Many of the older brothers and sisters who left the orphanage
- Xiaowen.

237
00:18:02,039 --> 00:18:06,439
- would come back and support us with their own money after they started working.
- This one's for you. Here, is it pretty?

238
00:18:06,439 --> 00:18:09,740
- That's how Xiaowen and I grew up.
- They're so pretty.

239
00:18:09,740 --> 00:18:14,819
Xiaowen is someone who will double the kindness he received.

240
00:18:14,819 --> 00:18:20,699
Ever since he was a child, he said he'd be like those older brothers and sisters when he grows up

241
00:18:20,699 --> 00:18:24,259
and support the younger brothers and sisters on his own.

242
00:18:25,419 --> 00:18:28,499
Xiaowen didn't want to come to Tieyuan before

243
00:18:28,499 --> 00:18:32,959
because he didn't want to trouble any more people.

244
00:18:32,959 --> 00:18:39,500
In that case, there would be too many people he'd need to repay for their kindness.

245
00:18:41,599 --> 00:18:43,240
"...no matter how old you are,

246
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:49,580
when you go out into the world, it is best to hold hands and stick together."

247
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:50,759
That's...

248
00:18:50,759 --> 00:18:54,799
No, no, no. I have to go and take care of it.

249
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,839
Why are you being so serious about going to the restroom?

250
00:18:58,839 --> 00:19:00,439
Come back soon!

251
00:19:00,439 --> 00:19:07,699
All right, Class. This is Robert Fulghum's short prose, Credo.

252
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:09,839
Xiaowen, I've made a decision.

253
00:19:09,839 --> 00:19:11,480
Gao Yang, what are you doing? This is our class.

254
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:13,480
Step aside.

255
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:16,879
Xiaowen, I can carry your responsibilities.

256
00:19:16,879 --> 00:19:20,279
What's mine is yours. I'll share half of my allowance with you right now.

257
00:19:20,279 --> 00:19:22,759
When I earn money in the future, I'll give you half of my salary, too.

258
00:19:22,759 --> 00:19:24,659
I mean what I said.

259
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:36,240
My classmates are doing self-studying. You should go back first.

260
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:40,259
Did you hear him? He told you to go back.

261
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:46,279
What kind of person is that?

262
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,900
That...

263
00:19:59,259 --> 00:20:01,319
I know that I'm quite childish right now.

264
00:20:01,319 --> 00:20:03,319
And I'm really unreliable.

265
00:20:03,319 --> 00:20:06,280
But I will become very reliable one day.

266
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:08,279
I mean what I said.

267
00:20:08,279 --> 00:20:10,219
Go back first.

268
00:20:12,079 --> 00:20:14,440
Don't disturb the other students from studying.

269
00:20:24,305 --> 00:20:27,599
Gao Yang, you were awesome today.

270
00:20:27,599 --> 00:20:31,480
If I'm going to write a novel later, I'll definitely make you my lead character.

271
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,599
It was all right.

272
00:20:32,599 --> 00:20:35,319
Gao Yang, did you go and bother Xiaowen again?

273
00:20:35,319 --> 00:20:37,319
No, just eat your food.

274
00:20:37,319 --> 00:20:40,412
Xiaowen, today's chicken drumsticks are really delicious. I'll give you some later.

275
00:20:50,759 --> 00:20:53,499
Xiaowen, let's sit over there.

276
00:20:53,900 --> 00:20:55,200
Stop looking.

277
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:57,219
Let's just eat.

278
00:20:57,219 --> 00:20:58,700
Let's go.

279
00:21:16,279 --> 00:21:18,640
Xiaowen, why are you eating with us?

280
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:21,200
Why don't you eat with Ms. Niu?

281
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:23,900
I should be eating with my friends of course.

282
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,739
Am I considered your friend then?

283
00:21:26,739 --> 00:21:27,720
Yes.

284
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:29,960
- What about me? What about me?
- What about me?

285
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:31,279
You're all my friends.

286
00:21:31,279 --> 00:21:33,920
Here, we have chicken drumsticks too.

287
00:21:38,519 --> 00:21:40,119
Well,

288
00:21:40,980 --> 00:21:45,080
I can share half of my salary with you in the future. But you have to share your chicken drumsticks with me today.

289
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:46,319
It's mine now.

290
00:21:46,319 --> 00:21:48,640
Zhao Jiabao, how dare you steal my drumstick.

291
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:51,820
Let me have a bite! Gao Yang, let me have a bite!

292
00:21:51,820 --> 00:21:53,920
Let me have a bite!

293
00:22:00,759 --> 00:22:02,620
You should reconsider.

294
00:22:02,620 --> 00:22:04,639
I've made my mind.

295
00:22:04,639 --> 00:22:08,480
I'm telling you, the vice principal really values you.

296
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:10,519
Are you sure you don't want to reconsider?

297
00:22:10,519 --> 00:22:13,739
But I still like the way you teach.

298
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:18,160
Well, since you put it that way, what else can I say?

299
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:21,079
Is it just because of me?

300
00:22:22,359 --> 00:22:24,160
My friends are in Class 3,

301
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:26,220
so that's why I want to go back.

302
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:29,380
All right. Go on in.

303
00:22:30,519 --> 00:22:33,039
Thank you, Mr. Wu.

304
00:22:41,519 --> 00:22:44,400
Xiaowen!

305
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,200
Very good.

306
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:54,720
I think it's a very nice way to welcome your classmate and unite the class.

307
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:55,640
Welcome home, Xiaowen!

308
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:58,900
Welcome, Xiaowen!

309
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:02,300
Alright, go back to your old seat.

310
00:23:02,300 --> 00:23:04,030
[Welcome home, Xiaowen]

311
00:23:08,519 --> 00:23:10,659
Where should I sit then?

312
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:14,480
Here we go.

313
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:17,520
Brother Bin, what hair style do you want?

314
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:18,680
I'll leave it up to you.

315
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:20,279
Make me look sharp. Not too disheveled.

316
00:23:20,279 --> 00:23:21,720
Of course.

317
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:23,359
It's rare for you to come.

318
00:23:23,359 --> 00:23:27,480
I must use all my hairdressing skills on your head

319
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:30,539
and make all women in Tieyuan swoon over your hairstyle.

320
00:23:30,539 --> 00:23:31,880
How's that?

321
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:34,100
The children are all here. What nonsense are you talking about?

322
00:23:34,100 --> 00:23:35,559
What do you mean nonsense?

323
00:23:35,559 --> 00:23:39,060
Aren't you grooming yourself for a blind date?

324
00:23:39,060 --> 00:23:41,340
What blind date?

325
00:23:41,340 --> 00:23:44,299
I'll be on TV this time.

326
00:23:44,299 --> 00:23:46,240
A blind date on TV?

327
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:49,160
Jenny, bring the best perm agent over here.

328
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:51,959
- Why must it always be related to blind dates?
- What is it?

329
00:23:51,959 --> 00:23:55,519
The TV station is coming to interview the Pre-Olympic track and field team of the No.3 High School. Got it?

330
00:23:55,519 --> 00:23:57,039
Pre-Olympic?

331
00:23:57,039 --> 00:24:03,739
I already made a pledge to turn out twenty elite athletes within 3 years.

332
00:24:03,739 --> 00:24:05,319
Twenty?

333
00:24:05,319 --> 00:24:06,799
Why don't you just go and become a deity?

334
00:24:06,799 --> 00:24:09,279
You're not even that good yourself.

335
00:24:09,279 --> 00:24:11,119
You're wrong about your dad.

336
00:24:11,119 --> 00:24:16,000
Your dad went to Beijing to participate in the National University Games on behalf of our province.

337
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,880
You hear that?

338
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:21,279
A hero is silent about his past glories, understand?

339
00:24:21,279 --> 00:24:22,920
Really?

340
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:25,400
You should tell them when you need to. Your son doesn't even know.

341
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:30,480
Was that the time you strained your leg muscle before you even competed?

342
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:32,960
Of course he can't mention that.

343
00:24:34,079 --> 00:24:37,359
I don't want to argue with ordinary people like you.

344
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:42,300
Xiaowen, this long-distance competition will be held in the city.

345
00:24:42,300 --> 00:24:45,000
You should familiarize yourself with the route later.

346
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:47,400
Don't waste time along the way.

347
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:49,000
Don't be nervous.

348
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,680
Being nervous is taboo, okay?

349
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,640
Don't worry.

350
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,839
Do you think Xiaowen is like you?

351
00:24:53,839 --> 00:24:55,760
Being nervous?

352
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:58,939
Xiaowen, I'll be waiting for you at the finish line.

353
00:24:58,939 --> 00:25:02,200
When you get first place, we will cheer, shout, and clap our hands for you.

354
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:04,419
We'll cheer and shout!

355
00:25:08,599 --> 00:25:12,200
Jiajia, Meng and I are passing all our luck to you.

356
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:15,537
Just take it easy on the day of your competition. You can surely win.

357
00:25:19,359 --> 00:25:22,359
I-I-I...

358
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,380
Wh-What's wrong, Jia?

359
00:25:24,380 --> 00:25:26,820
Are you nervous?

360
00:25:26,820 --> 00:25:29,079
No, I-I-I...

361
00:25:29,079 --> 00:25:31,040
I want to win first place!

362
00:25:31,040 --> 00:25:32,279
That's right!

363
00:25:32,279 --> 00:25:34,900
You have to be ambitious!

364
00:25:36,759 --> 00:25:38,960
Your classmates are so nice.

365
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:41,279
Jia has been so worried these days.

366
00:25:41,279 --> 00:25:43,160
She's afraid she won't be in the top 3.

367
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:46,540
Now that you're here, she seems so energetic.

368
00:25:46,540 --> 00:25:48,559
- Quickly eat some strawberries.
- Thank you, Auntie.

369
00:25:48,559 --> 00:25:50,640
- Thank you, Auntie.
- Don't mention it.

370
00:25:51,359 --> 00:25:56,139
Beibei, Meng, it's so good to have you both.

371
00:25:56,139 --> 00:25:58,319
I feel reassured when I see you both.

372
00:25:58,319 --> 00:26:00,759
Otherwise, I would be so worried.

373
00:26:00,759 --> 00:26:04,000
It's okay. We will be there to cheer you on the day of the competition.

374
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:07,600
Not only that, but after you win first place, we have a mysterious gift waiting for you!

375
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:08,839
What is it?

376
00:26:08,839 --> 00:26:10,400
What mysterious gift?

377
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:12,459
Why don't I know about it either?

378
00:26:12,459 --> 00:26:14,580
Don't ask. You'll know when you win first place.

379
00:26:14,580 --> 00:26:16,380
Open your mouth.

380
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:26,800
Brother Dawei, you're not playing?

381
00:26:27,279 --> 00:26:29,079
You guys go ahead.

382
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,640
Maybe we should go home.

383
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:32,920
Let's not distract Brother Dawei from studying.

384
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,880
Yes, why don't we... Why don't we just go home.

385
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,580
Forget it.

386
00:26:36,580 --> 00:26:37,920
I'll just study here.

387
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:40,060
I can't focus when I go home either.

388
00:26:41,279 --> 00:26:43,079
Brother Dazhang, you're here.

389
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:46,680
How's business lately?

390
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:48,000
It's been alright.

391
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,119
Everything's prepared for you inside.

392
00:26:49,119 --> 00:26:50,142
Okay.

393
00:26:50,142 --> 00:26:52,339
- Brother Dazhang.
- Brother Dazhang.
[The Night is Young Billiards Club]

394
00:26:52,799 --> 00:26:53,759
Hello, Brother Dazhang.

395
00:26:53,759 --> 00:26:57,659
Dawei, am I distracting you from your studies?

396
00:26:57,659 --> 00:26:59,119
No.

397
00:26:59,119 --> 00:27:02,759
Have you made a decision about what I told you last time?

398
00:27:02,759 --> 00:27:05,380
I... I want to take the college entrance exam first.

399
00:27:06,392 --> 00:27:08,200
My... my dad is urging me.

400
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,900
I don't have a choice.

401
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,540
That's alright.

402
00:27:12,540 --> 00:27:14,759
Taking the college entrance exam is a serious matter.

403
00:27:14,759 --> 00:27:19,340
Besides, you can always come back to me if you don't do well on the exam. Alright then.

404
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:20,900
Okay, you guys keep playing.

405
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,000
Let me know if there's anything.

406
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:24,320
- Thank you, Brother.
- Thank you, Brother.

407
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,880
Let's go.

408
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:39,640
Boss, the check, please.

409
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:42,699
Brother Dazhang has already paid your bill.

410
00:27:48,039 --> 00:27:50,020
Let's go.

411
00:27:50,020 --> 00:27:55,900
[The Night is Young Billiards Club]

412
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:08,640
Brother Dawei, what did Brother Dazhang want from you?

413
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:12,160
It's nothing, I'm just asking.

414
00:28:16,359 --> 00:28:19,620
He wants me to quit school and watch over his business.

415
00:28:19,620 --> 00:28:21,519
That's a good thing. Bring us along.

416
00:28:21,519 --> 00:28:23,359
Exactly. Brother Dazhang is running quite a few businesses.

417
00:28:23,359 --> 00:28:25,880
The supermarket, the beauty salon, the car wash, these are all his businesses.

418
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,440
Don't keep dwelling on those things.

419
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:29,340
Focus on your studies.

420
00:28:29,340 --> 00:28:31,920
A degree is better than anything.

421
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:39,979
Brother Dawei, are you studying so hard now because you want to impress Sister Wanwan?

422
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:43,240
Don't say things you shouldn't.

423
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:46,259
Sister Wanwan won't tutor Brother Dawei anymore.

424
00:28:46,780 --> 00:28:49,499
Let's go. Let's play basketball.

425
00:28:52,319 --> 00:28:53,900
- Tiger pounces on its prey!
- Gao Yang, you!

426
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:55,119
Tiger pounces on its prey.

427
00:28:55,119 --> 00:28:56,720
What are you doing?

428
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:59,740
Tiger pounces on its prey. Tiger pounces on its prey!

429
00:28:59,740 --> 00:29:01,680
Gao Yang, why aren't you going easy on me?

430
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,640
Why should I do that?

431
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,319
Isn't it because I'm a girl?

432
00:29:04,319 --> 00:29:06,839
So what if you're a girl? This is called respecting my opponent.

433
00:29:06,839 --> 00:29:08,640
I don't need you to respect me.

434
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:10,739
I want you to be nicer to me.

435
00:29:10,739 --> 00:29:12,679
Why should I be nice to you?

436
00:29:12,679 --> 00:29:14,039
Who are you being nice to instead of me then?

437
00:29:14,039 --> 00:29:16,720
Xiaowen. He's about to compete.

438
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:18,139
Then you're definitely not as nice as I am to Mi Jia.

439
00:29:18,139 --> 00:29:21,540
I've prepared a huge mysterious gift for her this time.

440
00:29:23,699 --> 00:29:25,619
- What is it?
- You'll know when it's time.

441
00:29:25,619 --> 00:29:28,680
Gao Yang, you can't drop the ball this time.

442
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:30,700
- We have to flaunt it on the day of the competition.
- Of course.

443
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:32,599
We have to beat the No. 1 and No. 6 High Schools' cheerleading teams!

444
00:29:32,599 --> 00:29:35,819
I'll go borrow a few drums from the drum corps.

445
00:29:35,819 --> 00:29:38,139
Sure, you're reliable.

446
00:29:38,139 --> 00:29:39,759
Don't waste your time on that.

447
00:29:39,759 --> 00:29:41,440
Focus on your studies. You don't have to cheer for me.

448
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:43,280
- No way!
- No way!

449
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:47,140
It's already the critical moment. We have to liven it up. We must top all the other schools!

450
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:50,160
That's right! Xiaowen, just focus on your competition.

451
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:52,039
Yes, we'll handle the atmosphere.

452
00:29:52,039 --> 00:29:53,279
It's already at this point, what's there to be shy about?

453
00:29:53,279 --> 00:29:59,920
- That's right. We must make your name and Mi Jia's name be heard throughout Tieyuan.
- Throughout Tieyuan.

454
00:30:01,459 --> 00:30:05,500
Fine, as long as you are both happy. I'll go train now.

455
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:07,320
- Keep it up!
- Keep it up!

456
00:30:08,530 --> 00:30:10,620
- Be gentle.
- Don't move.

457
00:30:10,620 --> 00:30:12,920
How do I use this?

458
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:19,340
Go for it! Go for it! Keep it up!

459
00:30:21,459 --> 00:30:23,159
Zeng Zhi.

460
00:30:27,559 --> 00:30:30,559
What are you doing? We are still in class.

461
00:30:30,559 --> 00:30:33,198
Go for it! Go for it!

462
00:30:33,198 --> 00:30:34,698
[Mi Jia, Xiaowen must win!]

463
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:40,440
Go, No. 3 High School! Go, Xiaowen!

464
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:42,118
Alright, class is over.

465
00:30:42,118 --> 00:30:44,079
- Take the mats back.
- Okay.

466
00:30:44,079 --> 00:30:46,280
Go, Xiaowen!

467
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:48,260
Great!

468
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:55,179
Alright, let's take a break.

469
00:30:55,179 --> 00:30:56,200
Mr. Li.

470
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:57,419
Gao Yang.

471
00:30:57,419 --> 00:30:59,480
What's going on here?

472
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:04,120
You mean the cheerleading team? Wanwan organized it. We all think it's pretty nice.

473
00:31:04,120 --> 00:31:07,919
We can have them dance at the finish line to cheer for our athletes.

474
00:31:07,919 --> 00:31:09,599
Why?

475
00:31:09,599 --> 00:31:12,140
Because... Why? You have a problem with that?

476
00:31:12,140 --> 00:31:13,579
I...

477
00:31:15,519 --> 00:31:18,499
- Why should Niu Wanwan be the lead?
- Exactly.

478
00:31:18,499 --> 00:31:21,540
I don't think she dances better than I do.

479
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:23,759
Classmate Jin Beibei,

480
00:31:23,759 --> 00:31:27,240
the cheerleading team belongs to the No. 3 High School. Anyone can join.

481
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:30,620
If you want to be the lead, we can compete for it.

482
00:31:30,620 --> 00:31:32,520
Fine, we'll compete.

483
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:35,859
Stop eating, everyone. Watch this!

484
00:31:35,859 --> 00:31:37,559
Five, six, seven, eight.

485
00:31:37,559 --> 00:31:40,839
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

486
00:31:40,839 --> 00:31:44,279
Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

487
00:31:44,279 --> 00:31:47,519
Three, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

488
00:31:47,519 --> 00:31:52,460
Four, two, three, four, five, six, seven, done!

489
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:56,060
What do you think? Don't I dance way better than Niu Wanwan?

490
00:31:59,799 --> 00:32:01,480
Well, let's all eat something.

491
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:04,859
Beibei, what was that dance? What kind of spasm was that?

492
00:32:04,859 --> 00:32:09,280
What do you know? Xiaowen, what do you think of my dance?

493
00:32:11,079 --> 00:32:12,579
Why don't you have some?

494
00:32:12,579 --> 00:32:16,580
Meng, Jia, what do you think?

495
00:32:18,070 --> 00:32:21,859
Beibei, this is your first time dancing after all.

496
00:32:21,859 --> 00:32:23,539
Good luck.

497
00:32:24,519 --> 00:32:28,190
Beibei, y-y-you used the same hand and foot.

498
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:33,279
I did? No way. I'll dance for you again.

499
00:32:34,599 --> 00:32:37,540
Five, six, seven, eight.
[No. 3 Tian Yuan Staff Accommodation]

500
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:48,260
Uncle Gao, what do you want to eat later?

501
00:32:49,419 --> 00:32:53,099
What's wrong, Doudou? Are you hungry? I'll go make something for you.

502
00:32:53,099 --> 00:32:59,019
There's no need. My mom said your cooking is terrible and left me some money. How about I take you to a restaurant?

503
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:03,800
Your mom said that?

504
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:08,740
Fine. How about I treat you to a meal at a restaurant later, okay?

505
00:33:11,039 --> 00:33:13,520
Is my mom pregnant?

506
00:33:15,140 --> 00:33:16,799
What?

507
00:33:16,799 --> 00:33:20,140
My parents went to the hospital. I think she's pregnant.

508
00:33:22,559 --> 00:33:25,400
When did that happen?

509
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,939
Old Jin never told me.

510
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:32,959
Well, Doudou... Do you want a brother or a sister?

511
00:33:32,959 --> 00:33:38,639
I do. If there's another child, we can bully Jin Beibei together.

512
00:33:38,639 --> 00:33:41,599
Don't think that way. Your sister is pretty nice to you.

513
00:33:41,599 --> 00:33:45,799
If you come to my house and be Gao Yang's little brother, he'll bully you to death. You know that?

514
00:33:45,799 --> 00:33:50,200
Then, Uncle Gao, when are you going to give Gao Yang a little brother?

515
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:54,619
Well, I'm putting my career first. I'm not thinking about that now.

516
00:33:54,619 --> 00:33:58,839
Well, Uncle Gao, you should get married soon.

517
00:33:58,839 --> 00:34:02,200
My class adviser is quite nice.

518
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:07,799
Your class adviser is Tian Meng's mom.

519
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,440
Do your homework.

520
00:34:16,780 --> 00:34:19,960
Thank you. Bye, bye.
[Tieyuan Municipal Hospital]

521
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:24,619
See? Look, my heart is beating at a good rhythm. It's powerful and strong.

522
00:34:24,619 --> 00:34:27,679
Yeah, right. The doctor said you should take a break.

523
00:34:27,679 --> 00:34:31,459
He said if you don't take care of a small problem, it'll turn into a big one.

524
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:34,519
I can't take a break. There's so much to do at school.

525
00:34:34,519 --> 00:34:37,580
Are you the only staff in school? You have to take a break even if you can't.

526
00:34:37,580 --> 00:34:41,020
It's even more upsetting at home! Beibei's grades...

527
00:34:42,079 --> 00:34:46,599
Well, Beibei just isn't cut out for studying. But Doudou isn't like her.

528
00:34:46,599 --> 00:34:51,259
Doudou has pretty good grades, right? Everyone has their own aspirations. They can't be forced, right?

529
00:34:51,259 --> 00:34:54,660
Maybe our Beibei is good at something else.

530
00:34:54,660 --> 00:34:59,339
She's good at sleeping. If you don't wake her, she can sleep forever until the end of time.

531
00:34:59,339 --> 00:35:01,759
All right, all right, Old Jin. Don't be angry.

532
00:35:01,759 --> 00:35:04,500
The doctor said you have to take your medicine on time.

533
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:08,000
Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

534
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,639
- Three, two, three, four...
- Beibei, Beibei.

535
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:12,919
What? Speak. Seven, eight.

536
00:35:12,919 --> 00:35:15,320
You don't have the talent. Stop being ridiculous.

537
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:19,120
No, I just can't swallow this anger.

538
00:35:19,120 --> 00:35:20,199
Four, two, three, four...

539
00:35:20,199 --> 00:35:22,919
Beibei, I think you should

540
00:35:22,919 --> 00:35:27,400
do s-some basic training first, like s-s-split kicks or something.

541
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:30,600
Split kicks? I know how to do that.

542
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:36,459
How's that?

543
00:35:36,459 --> 00:35:41,980
No, I mean... kick it up higher. Like... It's like...

544
00:35:42,679 --> 00:35:45,619
Like this. Kick it like this.

545
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,519
How can you kick so high?

546
00:35:48,519 --> 00:35:53,759
I-Is it really that hard? Just... just kick up. Kick up.

547
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:57,700
Meng, isn't that hard?

548
00:35:59,639 --> 00:36:00,880
It's alright.

549
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:02,880
Then you do one.

550
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,220
How come you know how to do that too?

551
00:36:11,220 --> 00:36:13,020
That's nothing.

552
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:18,000
Look.

553
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:20,619
- Exactly. It's nothing.
- Sit down!

554
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,640
You think you're all that.

555
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:28,609
- Is it really that hard?
- Is it really that hard?

556
00:36:56,036 --> 00:37:01,984
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

557
00:37:01,984 --> 00:37:09,349
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

558
00:37:09,349 --> 00:37:15,339
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

559
00:37:15,339 --> 00:37:21,379
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

560
00:37:21,379 --> 00:37:28,031
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

561
00:37:28,031 --> 00:37:33,671
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

562
00:37:33,671 --> 00:37:37,684
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

563
00:37:37,684 --> 00:37:41,106
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

564
00:37:41,106 --> 00:37:44,401
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

565
00:37:44,401 --> 00:37:51,061
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

566
00:37:51,061 --> 00:37:54,372
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

567
00:37:54,372 --> 00:37:58,584
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

568
00:37:58,584 --> 00:38:02,304
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

569
00:38:02,304 --> 00:38:10,364
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
